column1: IF ccr_estriol_d is MF 0 AND ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortol_d is MF 2 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortol_d is MF 2 AND ccr_zoa_dhe_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_etio_d is MF 1 AND ccr_sa_thb_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_thdoc_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
